if gs_leg_type_m = 5 or gs_leg_type_m = 6 then ! T-Leg, Double T-Leg material gs_leg_mat
addx -0.07/2 rotz 90 rotx 90
prism_ 9,0.07, -gs_leg_base_depth/2,0,15, gs_leg_base_depth/2,0,79, gs_leg_base_depth/2-0.04,0,900, 0,90,4000, gs_leg_base_depth/2-0.04,0.04,79, -gs_leg_base_depth/2+0.04,0.04,79, -gs_leg_base_depth/2+0.04,0,900, 0,90,4000, gs_leg_base_depth/2,0,15 del 1
